Name: pulmonary eosinophilia
Definition: A hypereosinophilic syndrome characterized by the accumulation of eosinophils in the lungs.

Name: disseminated eosinophilic collagen disease
Definition: A hypereosinophilic syndrome characterized by the accumulation of eosinophils in the lungs.

Name: eosinophilia-myalgia syndrome
Definition: A drug dependence that involves the continued use of hallucinogenic drugs despite problems related to use of the substance.
